      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK RAZOR (1) was below best last time at Maitland (26.05) in a Grade 5, finishing a 14 length sixth. Has already won two times from this draw. Looks a key chance on best form. WOOLGOOLGA GAL (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (22.68) in a NG at this track. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Should be about the money. KING DOUGIE (8) scored an on-pace win two back then gave a start and could manage only 6th at this track (19.64) last time. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Cannot be underestimated. TURBO MOUSE (4) form at this distance reads well.",
